Text: Appointment confirmed with V's Barbershop - Old City Philadelphia on Saturday, February 11, 2023 at 11:15AM. Visit mytime.com/u/PYtv7 to view details. We require two hours notice for cancellation or a fee may be charged. ATTENTION REGARDING KID'S CUTS: If your child cannot sit very still, our barbers are instructed not to cut their hair due to safety concerns. Please be advised, you may arrive at the shop with your child and they may be deemed too much of a risk to have their hair cut safely. Parents are expected to pay attention while their child is having their hair cut.
